'''聯盟冠軍賽最有價值球員獎'''（{{lang-en|League Championship Series Most Valuable Player Award}}）為大聯盟頒發給聯盟冠軍賽表現最為傑出的球員的獎項。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.startribune.com/blogs/56922227.html?elr=KArksi8cyaiUBP7hUiD3aPc:_Yyc:aUU|title=Thursday (Derek Jeter over Joe Mauer for MVP?) edition: Wha' Happened?|last=Rand|first=Michael|date=2009-09-03|work=Minneapolis Star-Tribune|access-date=2009-09-12}}</ref>國家聯盟於1977年便開始頒發此獎項，[[達斯蒂·貝克|達斯蒂·貝克]]為第一位獲獎者；而美國聯盟到1980年才開始頒發此獎項，[[法蘭克·懷特|法蘭克·懷特]]為美聯首位獲獎者。截至2020年止，一共有10位獲得聯盟冠軍賽MVP的球員最終入選名人堂。

[[史蒂夫·賈維|史蒂夫·賈維]]、[[戴夫·史都華|戴夫·史都華]]和[[奧勒爾·赫西瑟|奧勒爾·赫西瑟]]成為唯三位在兩個不同球隊拿下聯盟冠軍賽MVP的球員。另外，[[弗瑞德·林恩|弗瑞德·林恩]]、Mike Scott和Jeffrey Leonard等三位選手當時雖然該所屬球隊輸球，不過最終仍順利獲獎。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CAL/1982.shtml|title=1982 California Angels Batting, Pitching, and Fielding Statistics|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2009-09-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/HOU/1986.shtml|title=1986 Houston Astros Batting, Pitching, and Fielding Statistics|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2009-09-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/SFG/1987.shtml|title=1987 San Francisco Giants Batting, Pitching, and Fielding Statistics|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2009-09-05}}</ref>

賈維、Leonard、[[亞伯特·普荷斯|亞伯特·普荷斯]]和[[藍迪·亞羅薩倫納|藍迪·亞羅薩倫納]]都在系列賽敲出4轟。<ref name="garvey"/><ref name="leonard"/><ref name="pujols"/><ref name="arozarena">{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2020/10/18/rays-randy-arozarena-named-alcs-mvp/3701461001/|author=Bob Nightengale|title=With four ALCS homers, Rays outfielder Randy Arozarena named series MVP|work=USAToday.com|date=2020-10-18|access-date=2020-10-18}}</ref>

[[奧蘭多·赫南德茲|奧蘭多·赫南德茲]]和Liván Hernández成為大聯盟目前唯一一位皆獲獎的兄弟檔。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/h/hernaor01.shtml|title=Orlando Hernández Statistics and History|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2009-09-05}}</ref>而Mike Boddicker、Liván Hernández、[[麥可·瓦卡|麥可·瓦卡]]和亞羅薩倫納都在菜鳥年便拿下此獎。<ref>[https://www.sbnation.com/mlb/2013/10/19/4854492/michael-wacha-mvp-nlcs-cardinals-dodgers Michael Wacha named NLCS MVP]</ref><ref name="arozarena"/>

